Enter the Roll No: 1
Enter the Name: Gurumoorthy
Enter the Roll No: 2
Enter the Name: Naruto Uzumaki
Enter the Roll No: 3
Enter the Name: Itachi Uchiha
Enter the Roll No: 2
Enter the Name: Naruto Uzumaki
Enter the Roll No: 5
Enter the Name: Kakashi Hatake

